1
00:00:09,209 --> 00:00:10,676
[theme music]

2
00:01:52,209 --> 00:01:53,676
[diabolical laughter]

3
00:01:57,676 --> 00:01:59,176
[gasps]

4
00:02:02,309 --> 00:02:04,176
-It can't be!

5
00:02:04,209 --> 00:02:06,543
[diabolical laughter]

6
00:02:06,576 --> 00:02:10,309
-I can tell when you're
bluffing, my dear.

7
00:02:10,343 --> 00:02:14,409
And right now, you're
already finished!

8
00:02:14,443 --> 00:02:16,409
[clink]

9
00:02:16,443 --> 00:02:17,909
[fast breathing]

10
00:02:32,843 --> 00:02:36,076
-[chuckling] Poor little thing.

11
00:02:36,109 --> 00:02:40,643
Look at her, trembling
like a newborn pup.

12
00:02:40,676 --> 00:02:42,443
All right, Kabuto.

13
00:02:42,476 --> 00:02:45,709
Get rid of her, but try
not to let her suffer.

14
00:02:45,743 --> 00:02:47,409
-Right.

15
00:02:47,443 --> 00:02:48,809
[footsteps]

16
00:02:51,676 --> 00:02:54,543
SAKURA: Sasuke!

17
00:02:54,576 --> 00:02:57,276
I'll do anything
for you, Sasuke!

18
00:02:57,309 --> 00:02:59,509
So, please!

19
00:02:59,543 --> 00:03:00,876
I'm begging you!

20
00:03:00,909 --> 00:03:04,476
Don't walk away!

21
00:03:04,509 --> 00:03:07,143
-You haven't changed.

22
00:03:07,176 --> 00:03:09,243
You're still annoying.

23
00:03:09,276 --> 00:03:10,676
-Don't leave me!

24
00:03:14,643 --> 00:03:15,109
-Sakura.

25
00:03:18,109 --> 00:03:22,543
Thank you for everything.

26
00:03:22,576 --> 00:03:25,476
[thump]

27
00:03:25,509 --> 00:03:25,976
-Sasuke.

28
00:03:32,109 --> 00:03:33,476
Wait!

29
00:03:33,509 --> 00:03:34,909
-Hmm?

30
00:03:34,943 --> 00:03:36,343
Yes, my dear?

31
00:03:36,376 --> 00:03:37,709
You had something to say?

32
00:03:37,743 --> 00:03:40,143
-Hold on a minute!

33
00:03:40,176 --> 00:03:42,109
[chuckles]

34
00:03:42,143 --> 00:03:43,109
-Sasuke.

35
00:03:43,143 --> 00:03:45,076
Where is he?

36
00:03:45,109 --> 00:03:49,476
You couldn't have-- you couldn't
have taken his body already!

37
00:03:49,509 --> 00:03:53,009
-No need to hide it
any longer, I suppose.

38
00:03:53,043 --> 00:03:55,143
It's fine, Kabuto.

39
00:03:55,176 --> 00:03:57,109
Go ahead and tell her.

40
00:03:57,143 --> 00:04:00,043
[footsteps]

41
00:04:00,076 --> 00:04:01,576
[door creaking shut]

42
00:04:06,076 --> 00:04:09,609
-Unfortunately, Sasuke was
a little late getting here,

43
00:04:09,643 --> 00:04:12,609
and Lord Orochimaru
wasn't able to wait.

44
00:04:12,643 --> 00:04:15,376
He had to make do
with another vessel.

45
00:04:15,409 --> 00:04:17,976
-So, Sasuke's all
right, then, isn't he?

46
00:04:18,009 --> 00:04:20,009
And he's somewhere
in this building!

47
00:04:20,043 --> 00:04:22,943
-Lord Orochimaru gave
Uchiha the curse mark

48
00:04:22,976 --> 00:04:27,776
to prepare him to be ready for
my lord's next incarnation.

49
00:04:27,809 --> 00:04:31,509
The problem is, not
everyone can bear

50
00:04:31,543 --> 00:04:34,743
the burden of the curse mark.

51
00:04:34,776 --> 00:04:36,209
[crunching]

52
00:04:42,543 --> 00:04:43,009
-Nngh!

53
00:04:48,343 --> 00:04:49,343
-Impossible!

54
00:04:49,376 --> 00:04:51,876
There's no way that
Sasuke could be--

55
00:04:51,909 --> 00:04:53,676
-I'm afraid so.

56
00:04:53,709 --> 00:04:56,843
Sasuke couldn't handle the curse
mark and now he's a memory.

57
00:04:56,876 --> 00:04:58,509
-You're lying!

58
00:04:58,543 --> 00:05:00,776
I don't believe you.

59
00:05:00,809 --> 00:05:03,176
It has to be a lie!

60
00:05:03,209 --> 00:05:06,076
-[sighing] Oh, come now.

61
00:05:06,109 --> 00:05:08,609
What on Earth have
I to gain by lying?

62
00:05:08,643 --> 00:05:12,776
I mean, in another minute
here, you'll be dead.

63
00:05:12,809 --> 00:05:16,643
Since you're in such a hurry
to see him, let me help you.

64
00:05:16,676 --> 00:05:20,276
You can spend eternity
together in the afterlife.

65
00:05:37,676 --> 00:05:40,609
[chuckling]

66
00:05:48,109 --> 00:05:50,576
-Sasuke.

67
00:05:50,609 --> 00:05:52,109
-Sakura!

68
00:05:52,143 --> 00:05:54,176
[kring]

69
00:05:54,209 --> 00:05:55,409
-Nngh.

70
00:05:55,443 --> 00:05:58,343
-Sakura, don't believe a
word out of this guy's mouth.

71
00:05:58,376 --> 00:05:58,909
Nngh.

72
00:05:58,943 --> 00:06:00,909
He's full of it!

73
00:06:00,943 --> 00:06:01,876
-Naruto!

74
00:06:01,909 --> 00:06:04,343
-Well, what do you
know about that!

75
00:06:04,376 --> 00:06:07,676
I just figured you'd
drowned by now, Naruto.

76
00:06:07,709 --> 00:06:09,709
-Whenever I make a promise,
I don't ever give up!

77
00:06:09,743 --> 00:06:11,643
That's my ninja way, pal!

78
00:06:11,676 --> 00:06:13,976
And until we get Sasuke
back, nothing on Earth

79
00:06:14,009 --> 00:06:15,809
is gonna stop me!

80
00:06:15,843 --> 00:06:17,109
-Hmm.

81
00:06:17,143 --> 00:06:18,876
Interesting.

82
00:06:18,909 --> 00:06:20,343
[shing]

83
00:06:20,376 --> 00:06:21,843
[thunking]

84
00:06:21,876 --> 00:06:25,309
-Sakura, you find
a place to hide.

85
00:06:25,343 --> 00:06:26,776
[shing]

86
00:06:26,809 --> 00:06:28,743
-Shadow Clone Jutsu!

87
00:06:28,776 --> 00:06:32,209
[poof]

88
