-Hey, four eyes!
[laughing] Hey, over here!

89
00:06:36,476 --> 00:06:38,143
I mean here!

90
00:06:38,176 --> 00:06:40,109
What are you looking at?

91
00:06:40,143 --> 00:06:41,076
I'm right over here.

92
00:06:41,109 --> 00:06:44,476
[interposing voices]

93
00:06:44,509 --> 00:06:44,976
-Hmm?

94
00:06:45,009 --> 00:06:46,409
Keh!

95
00:06:46,443 --> 00:06:47,876
[shing]

96
00:06:47,909 --> 00:06:48,876
[grunting]

97
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:51,109
[shing]

98
00:06:51,143 --> 00:06:53,043
[grunting]

99
00:06:53,076 --> 00:06:53,543
-Huh?

100
00:06:53,576 --> 00:06:55,509
Nngh!

101
00:06:55,543 --> 00:07:00,376
--[laughing] Looks like
you're all out of kunai!

102
00:07:00,409 --> 00:07:05,876
I hope you're ready, 'cause I'm
gonna wipe the floor with you!

103
00:07:05,909 --> 00:07:08,843
[roaring]

104
00:07:08,876 --> 00:07:10,309
[kring]

105
00:07:15,276 --> 00:07:16,743
[grunting]

106
00:07:21,709 --> 00:07:24,143
-These clones are
really irritating!

107
00:07:24,176 --> 00:07:29,343
Fire Style, Mystic
Flames Dance Jutsu!

108
00:07:29,376 --> 00:07:30,809
[whoosh]

109
00:07:30,843 --> 00:07:31,809
CLONES: Ahhh!

110
00:07:40,109 --> 00:07:43,076
[popping]

111
00:07:43,109 --> 00:07:48,543
-[chuckling] Huh?

112
00:07:48,576 --> 00:07:50,543
[buzzing]

113
00:07:50,576 --> 00:07:52,043
[gasps]

114
00:07:52,076 --> 00:07:54,043
-Too little, too late!

115
00:07:54,076 --> 00:07:56,043
Rasengan!

116
00:07:56,076 --> 00:07:58,509
Aaugh!

117
00:07:58,543 --> 00:08:00,009
[roars]

118
00:08:00,043 --> 00:08:01,509
[yells]

119
00:08:01,543 --> 00:08:04,509
[thudding]

120
00:08:04,543 --> 00:08:06,476
-Nngh!

121
00:08:06,509 --> 00:08:08,443
[labored breathing]

122
00:08:08,476 --> 00:08:09,943
[pop]

123
00:08:09,976 --> 00:08:10,938
-Naruto!

124
00:08:14,676 --> 00:08:16,509
[footsteps]

125
00:08:16,543 --> 00:08:19,143
-If you and Orochimaru
are here, then Sasuke

126
00:08:19,176 --> 00:08:21,643
is probably here somewhere, too.

127
00:08:21,676 --> 00:08:22,976
We want the truth.

128
00:08:23,009 --> 00:08:25,376
Now!

129
00:08:25,409 --> 00:08:27,309
[chuckles]

130
00:08:27,343 --> 00:08:29,743
[gasps]

131
00:08:29,776 --> 00:08:33,043
-What-- what the
heck is going on?

132
00:08:33,076 --> 00:08:34,043
What did you do?

133
00:08:34,076 --> 00:08:35,909
I can't move anymore!

134
00:08:35,943 --> 00:08:37,776
-Heh.

135
00:08:37,809 --> 00:08:40,143
Take a good look at yourself.

136
00:08:40,176 --> 00:08:42,443
Notice anything funny?

137
00:08:42,476 --> 00:08:46,443
--[gasping] What
have you done to me?

138
00:08:46,476 --> 00:08:49,076
-Those threads wrapped around
you are made of chakra.

139
00:08:49,109 --> 00:08:52,409
-Made of chakra?

140
00:08:52,443 --> 00:08:55,309
-When you came in
for your big finish,

141
00:08:55,343 --> 00:08:58,709
I was able to weave
them around your body.

142
00:08:58,743 --> 00:09:01,976
Now, look carefully.

143
00:09:02,009 --> 00:09:03,843
See where those threads lead to?

144
00:09:03,876 --> 00:09:05,243
[gasps]

145
00:09:08,676 --> 00:09:10,143
-That's right.

146
00:09:10,176 --> 00:09:18,943
These chakra threads are wrapped
up in the chambers of my heart.

147
00:09:18,976 --> 00:09:22,443
What's more, Naruto, the
threat is weaving its way

148
00:09:22,476 --> 00:09:24,276
into your body as well.

149
00:09:24,309 --> 00:09:25,743
Into your heart.

150
00:09:25,776 --> 00:09:28,809
All of the internal organs
that keep you functioning.

151
00:09:28,843 --> 00:09:30,176
[gasps]

152
00:09:30,209 --> 00:09:32,009
[heart beating]

153
00:09:32,043 --> 00:09:33,043
-Listen.

154
00:09:33,076 --> 00:09:34,943
You can hear it, can't you?

155
00:09:34,976 --> 00:09:36,709
Our heart rates
are synchronizing.

156
00:09:36,743 --> 00:09:40,743
[inhaling] In a moment,
they will beat as one.

157
00:09:40,776 --> 00:09:42,743
-[gasping] Are you crazy?

158
00:09:42,776 --> 00:09:43,743
-Naruto!

159
00:09:43,776 --> 00:09:44,743
-Nngh!

160
00:09:44,776 --> 00:09:45,676
-Mmm.

161
00:09:45,709 --> 00:09:47,676
No use struggling.

162
00:09:47,709 --> 00:09:50,509
Those threads are made
up of pure chakra.

163
00:09:50,543 --> 00:09:52,409
Nothing you do can break them.

164
00:09:52,443 --> 00:09:53,576
[gasps]

165
00:09:56,576 --> 00:09:58,009
-There.

166
00:09:58,043 --> 00:10:02,243
Now our hearts are
totally in sync.

167
00:10:02,276 --> 00:10:06,309
The chakra in these threads has
linked my circulatory system

168
00:10:06,343 --> 00:10:07,976
directly to your own.

169
00:10:08,009 --> 00:10:10,843
Your heart's entirely
under my control.

170
00:10:10,876 --> 00:10:11,776
NARUTO: Ugh!

171
00:10:11,809 --> 00:10:13,209
It's no use.

172
00:10:13,243 --> 00:10:15,109
Even though it's mine.

173
00:10:15,143 --> 00:10:18,109
-If my heart should be
faster, then your heart

174
00:10:18,143 --> 00:10:20,209
will beat right along with it.

175
00:10:20,243 --> 00:10:24,109
And of course you realize when
my heartbeat comes to an end,

176
00:10:24,143 --> 00:10:27,009
so, too, does yours.

177
00:10:27,043 --> 00:10:28,509
[gasps]

178
00:10:28,543 --> 00:10:29,143
-Don't!

179
00:10:29,176 --> 00:10:30,276
What's the point?

180
00:10:30,309 --> 00:10:32,376
If you stop your heart,
then you'll die, too!

181
00:10:32,409 --> 00:10:33,909
-Yes, I'll die.

182
00:10:33,943 --> 00:10:37,043
But then, it hardly matters now.

183
00:10:37,076 --> 00:10:39,976
I've already promised my
body to Lord Orochimaru

184
00:10:40,009 --> 00:10:41,076
to use at his disposal.

185
00:10:45,443 --> 00:10:45,943
Aaugh!

186
00:10:54,876 --> 00:10:56,276
[loud heartbeats]

187
00:10:56,309 --> 00:10:57,776
[gasps]

188
00:11:02,743 --> 00:11:06,643
-What-- what exactly are
you planning on doing?

189
00:11:06,676 --> 00:11:08,109
-Heh.

190
00:11:08,143 --> 00:11:11,509
Now all I have to do is squeeze.

191
00:11:11,543 --> 00:11:14,909
Then I'll die and so will you.

192
00:11:22,304 --> 00:11:25,304
Now all I have to do is squeeze.

193
00:11:25,337 --> 00:11:27,137
And then I'll die.

194
00:11:27,170 --> 00:11:29,104
And so will you.

195
00:11:29,137 --> 00:11:30,537
Let's go.

196
00:11:30,570 --> 00:11:32,937
You can come with me.

197
00:11:32,970 --> 00:11:34,370
[squish]

198
00:11:34,404 --> 00:11:35,337
-Aaugh!

199
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:36,004
-Naruto!

200
00:11:36,037 --> 00:11:37,304
-So, how's it feel?

201
00:11:37,337 --> 00:11:40,470
Having your heart crushed
from inside your own chest?

202
00:11:40,504 --> 00:11:44,804
Don't worry, you'll be out
of your misery soon enough.

203
00:11:44,837 --> 00:11:46,270
[squish]

204
00:11:46,304 --> 00:11:49,204
-Aaugh!

205
00:11:49,237 --> 00:11:50,670
[shing]

206
00:11:50,704 --> 00:11:53,137
-That's enough!

207
00:11:53,170 --> 00:11:55,070
-Don't be such a fool!

208
00:11:55,104 --> 00:11:58,404
If you take me out, then
Naruto goes with me.

209
00:11:58,437 --> 00:11:59,637
-I have a better idea.

210
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:02,037
Let's just do this!

211
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:02,970
Nngh!

212
00:12:03,004 --> 00:12:06,837
[splat]

213
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:08,970
-You're wasting your time.

214
00:12:09,004 --> 00:12:11,404
The thread is spun from chakra.

215
00:12:11,437 --> 00:12:13,837
It can't be severed.

216
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:14,337
-Aaugh!

217
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:21,837
--[chuckling] Even lady
Tsunade, with all her strength,

218
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:24,304
would be powerless to break it.

219
00:12:24,337 --> 00:12:24,804
-Nngh!

220
00:12:30,304 --> 00:12:31,704
What do I do?

221
00:12:31,737 --> 00:12:33,737
What do I do?

222
00:12:33,770 --> 00:12:36,704
Naruto is suffering
right in front of me

223
00:12:36,737 --> 00:12:38,170
and I'm helpless to stop it!

224
00:12:41,704 --> 00:12:43,104
-Don't you worry, Sakura.

225
00:12:45,904 --> 00:12:47,604
I don't care what happens.

226
00:12:47,637 --> 00:12:51,770
Nothing's gonna stop
me, not 'til I've

227
00:12:51,804 --> 00:12:54,970
delivered on my promise!

228
00:12:55,004 --> 00:12:59,304
-This ridiculous
bravado ends here!

229
00:12:59,337 --> 00:13:02,070
Time to leave this mortal coil.

230
00:13:02,104 --> 00:13:05,537
Then you can finally
see your beloved Sasuke.

231
00:13:05,570 --> 00:13:07,104
[squish]

232
00:13:07,137 --> 00:13:09,570
-Aaugh!

233
00:13:09,604 --> 00:13:11,037
[heart beating faster]

234
00:13:21,004 --> 00:13:22,970
-Nnngh!

235
00:13:23,004 --> 00:13:25,937
-Aaugh!

236
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:27,937
-Naruto!

237
00:13:27,970 --> 00:13:30,904
-Sakura!

238
00:13:30,937 --> 00:13:31,904
-Sasame!

239
00:13:31,937 --> 00:13:34,904
-Sakura, take this tag.

240
00:13:34,937 --> 00:13:36,870
Wrap your kunai in it.

241
00:13:39,904 --> 00:13:41,337
[buzz]

242
00:13:44,837 --> 00:13:45,804
-Augh!

243
00:13:45,837 --> 00:13:49,270
[slash]

244
00:13:49,304 --> 00:13:50,770
-Aaugh!

245
00:13:50,804 --> 00:13:51,937
-Aaugh!

246
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:52,437
[thud]

247
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:52,937
-Naruto!

248
00:13:55,737 --> 00:13:57,604
Naruto?

249
00:13:57,637 --> 00:13:59,604
Naruto?

250
00:13:59,637 --> 00:14:01,304
Hey.

251
00:14:01,337 --> 00:14:02,804
Are you OK?

252
00:14:02,837 --> 00:14:05,070
Naruto!

253
00:14:05,104 --> 00:14:06,737
It can't be!

254
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:08,670
No, please!

255
00:14:08,704 --> 00:14:10,604
You can't!

256
00:14:10,637 --> 00:14:12,570
[crying] Naruto!

257
00:14:20,604 --> 00:14:22,504
[heart beating]

258
00:14:22,537 --> 00:14:23,004
-Huh?

259
00:14:26,770 --> 00:14:28,537
-Oh yeah!

260
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:30,037
Nothin' gets the
heart crankin' like

261
00:14:30,070 --> 00:14:31,337
the touch of a beautiful woman.

262
00:14:34,170 --> 00:14:34,637
-Jerk!

263
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:36,037
[clang]

264
00:14:36,070 --> 00:14:38,370
-I can't believe I
wasted my tears on you!

265
00:14:38,404 --> 00:14:39,970
-Sorry, Sakura.

266
00:14:40,004 --> 00:14:43,670
-Man, you really are
hopeless, aren't you?

267
00:14:43,704 --> 00:14:45,904
[laughs]

268
00:14:45,937 --> 00:14:46,837
-So, wait.

269
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:48,904
Sasame-- What are
you doing here?

270
00:14:48,937 --> 00:14:51,304
-Oh, well, I was just--

271
00:14:51,337 --> 00:14:53,137
-I'm just glad she
showed up when she did,

272
00:14:53,170 --> 00:14:54,804
otherwise I wouldn't be here.

273
00:14:54,837 --> 00:14:56,404
-You can say that again.

274
00:14:56,437 --> 00:14:57,437
-Huh?

275
00:14:57,470 --> 00:14:59,337
What do you guys mean?

276
00:14:59,370 --> 00:15:01,504
-That pit coming Gamakichi
and I were caught in

