started filling up with water.

278
00:15:03,937 --> 00:15:05,370
[water rushing]

279
00:15:14,204 --> 00:15:17,104
-Guh!

280
00:15:17,137 --> 00:15:22,504
OK, I think this is the lid!

281
00:15:22,537 --> 00:15:25,904
[grunting] Come on!

282
00:15:34,370 --> 00:15:36,204
When the water
reached the top, I

283
00:15:36,237 --> 00:15:38,104
pushed against the ceiling
as hard as I could,

284
00:15:38,137 --> 00:15:39,737
but it wouldn't budge.

285
00:15:45,337 --> 00:15:48,170
SASAME: Master Jiraiya told
me to head for the place

286
00:15:48,204 --> 00:15:50,070
where he met up with Hanzaki.

287
00:15:50,104 --> 00:15:54,337
[gasping] But I was so
worried about Arashi,

288
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:56,004
I just had to come.

289
00:15:56,037 --> 00:15:57,470
[splash]

290
00:16:00,937 --> 00:16:09,837
-[gasping] Is that you, Naruto?

291
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:12,404
-Hey, thanks a lot, doll.

292
00:16:12,437 --> 00:16:14,637
-Tha-- that frog
just spoke to me!

293
00:16:17,570 --> 00:16:20,837
-Now that I think about it,
I guess it was kind of silly

294
00:16:20,870 --> 00:16:23,737
trying to open that thing
just by pushing on it.

295
00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:24,970
-Ugh.

296
00:16:25,004 --> 00:16:28,870
But my kunai wasn't cutting
those threads at all.

297
00:16:28,904 --> 00:16:31,470
So how come it worked after
I wrapped your tag around it?

298
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:37,504
-Because the chakra thread
is one of the Fuma Clan's

299
00:16:37,537 --> 00:16:40,070
most guarded ninja techniques.

300
00:16:40,104 --> 00:16:41,470
-The Fuma Clan's?

301
00:16:41,504 --> 00:16:43,304
-Oh, that explains it!

302
00:16:43,337 --> 00:16:46,570
So wait a minute, who
the heck is this guy?

303
00:16:46,604 --> 00:16:48,070
[crumbling]

304
00:16:48,104 --> 00:16:49,470
-Huh?

305
00:16:49,504 --> 00:16:49,970
Hmm.

306
00:16:56,970 --> 00:17:00,204
SASAME AND SAKURA: [gasping]

307
00:17:00,237 --> 00:17:02,737
-Well, what do you know?

308
00:17:02,770 --> 00:17:03,770
It was you again.

309
00:17:07,604 --> 00:17:09,937
-Master Kagaro.

310
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:11,837
She's a Fuma jounin.

311
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:13,270
-What is it?

312
00:17:13,304 --> 00:17:16,170
What's wrong?

313
00:17:16,204 --> 00:17:18,404
-Hey, Sasame.

314
00:17:18,437 --> 00:17:19,370
It's all right.

315
00:17:19,404 --> 00:17:20,837
Don't be frightened.

316
00:17:20,870 --> 00:17:24,437
Lord Orochimaru has simple
given me a second life.

317
00:17:24,470 --> 00:17:25,404
-Are you kidding?

318
00:17:25,437 --> 00:17:26,970
That snake's playing
you for a fool!

319
00:17:27,004 --> 00:17:28,704
-Where are they hiding Sasuke?

320
00:17:28,737 --> 00:17:31,404
-Yeah, and what about
Sasame's cousin, huh?

321
00:17:31,437 --> 00:17:34,504
Where are they keeping Arashi?

322
00:17:34,537 --> 00:17:38,237
-Lord Orochimaru is our savior.

323
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,837
The honorable Fuma
Clan has fallen,

324
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:42,504
but he will lift us up again.

325
00:17:42,537 --> 00:17:45,870
Higher than all other shinobi.

326
00:17:45,904 --> 00:17:48,504
-Are you still
spouting that trash?

327
00:17:48,537 --> 00:17:49,370
Enough, already!

328
00:17:49,404 --> 00:17:52,304
Tell Sasame where her cousin is!

329
00:17:52,337 --> 00:17:53,737
[chuckles]

330
00:17:59,537 --> 00:18:01,904
-Huh?

331
00:18:01,937 --> 00:18:03,070
-Over there?

332
00:18:03,104 --> 00:18:04,704
Is that where they are?

333
00:18:08,837 --> 00:18:11,504
-You and your cousin, Sasame.

334
00:18:11,537 --> 00:18:15,537
You were always so close to
one another, weren't you?

335
00:18:15,570 --> 00:18:18,404
[heart beats]

336
00:18:18,437 --> 00:18:21,804
-It would be better if
you didn't see him now.

337
00:18:21,837 --> 00:18:22,804
[gasps]

338
00:18:22,837 --> 00:18:24,304
[heard beats]

339
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:34,237
[heart beats slow]

340
00:18:39,737 --> 00:18:46,970
-[gasping] Master Kagero.

341
00:18:51,770 --> 00:18:53,204
-Well, Sasame.

342
00:18:53,237 --> 00:18:54,570
What you want to do?

343
00:18:54,604 --> 00:18:56,304
-You can wait here, if you want.

344
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:03,370
-I have to see him.

345
00:19:03,404 --> 00:19:06,104
I don't care what awaits
me beyond that door!

346
00:19:06,137 --> 00:19:09,770
I came to find Arashi and
that's what I'm going to do!

347
00:19:09,804 --> 00:19:10,604
-Mmhmm!

348
00:19:10,637 --> 00:19:12,870
I like your guts, girly!

349
00:19:12,904 --> 00:19:13,704
-Right!

350
00:19:13,737 --> 00:19:15,570
We forge on together, then!

351
00:19:15,604 --> 00:19:16,104
-Yeah!

352
00:19:16,137 --> 00:19:17,370
Let's do it.

353
00:19:25,170 --> 00:19:26,137
MALE SPEAKER: Sasame.

354
00:19:32,504 --> 00:19:35,337
-There could be some
sort of trap here.

355
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:36,937
-Just leave it to me.

356
00:19:36,970 --> 00:19:38,370
[door creaks open]

357
00:19:46,137 --> 00:19:50,004
[footsteps]

358
00:19:50,037 --> 00:19:50,504
-Orochimaru!

359
00:19:56,837 --> 00:20:00,237
-It's good of you
to come, Sasame.

360
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:02,237
-Where's my cousin?

361
00:20:11,737 --> 00:20:16,704
-[gasping] Arashi!

362
00:20:16,737 --> 00:20:17,204
Arashi!

363
00:20:21,204 --> 00:20:22,037
What's wrong, Arashi?

364
00:20:25,004 --> 00:20:27,637
-You're mistaken.

365
00:20:27,670 --> 00:20:31,137
I'm not the Arashi you knew.

366
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:33,104
[squishing]

367
00:20:33,137 --> 00:20:34,570
[bursting]

368
00:20:34,604 --> 00:20:35,070
-Ahh!

369
00:20:41,037 --> 00:20:42,470
[roaring]

370
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:56,270
-What the heck is
going on around here?

371
00:20:56,304 --> 00:20:59,704
-The bodies and the skills
of the Fuma Clan's strongest

372
00:20:59,737 --> 00:21:02,670
jounin have merged
and I have been

373
00:21:02,704 --> 00:21:06,404
reborn as the ultimate shinobi!

374
00:21:06,437 --> 00:21:12,037
Now let me show you the
most powerful ninjutsu

375
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:15,437
you've ever seen, Sasame!

376
00:21:15,470 --> 00:21:17,370
-Arashi!

377
00:21:17,404 --> 00:21:19,804
What have you done to yourself?

378
00:21:19,837 --> 00:21:22,970
-Orochimaru, you lousy snake!

379
00:21:23,004 --> 00:21:26,558
I won't forgive him for
this, no matter what!

380
00:21:30,631 --> 00:21:32,098
[theme music]

381
00:23:03,165 --> 00:23:04,331
SAKURA: I'm sorry.

382
00:23:04,365 --> 00:23:05,998
Forgive me, Naruto.

383
00:23:06,031 --> 00:23:08,065
I haven't been a
help you at all.

384
00:23:08,098 --> 00:23:10,531
The only thing I do
is weigh you down.

385
00:23:10,565 --> 00:23:13,131
I haven't changed one bit.

386
00:23:13,165 --> 00:23:18,031
But Naruto, Sasame, I've
learned so much from you both.

387
00:23:18,065 --> 00:23:20,598
That's why I want to change
the kind of person I am.

388
00:23:20,631 --> 00:23:24,498
This time, this time it's
my turn to give it my all.

389
00:23:24,531 --> 00:23:27,293
Next time, "Sakura's
Determination!"

390
00:23:30,798 --> 00:23:34,298
[theme music]

